HEADWORD: Drawplate
<hw>Draw"plate`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A hardened steel
plate having a hole, or a gradation of conical holes, through which
wires are drawn to be reduced and elongated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

